    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Bronze Age T-shaped stone monuments, found on Minorca in the Balearic Islands, consisting of a vertical slab with a horizontal slab mounted at the top. These are believed to be places of religious significance, and are usually found in a complex of other structures.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
